BY TIMOTHY AGBOR An unspecified number of people have been injured while some might have feared killed after a passenger train crushed a Lagos State Government staff bus at PWD area of the state. The accident happened few minutes after 7am on Thursday. The spokesperson for the Lagos State Traffic Management Authority, Taofiq Adebayo, said rescue operation was ongoing. “The accident recorded many casualties as the staff bus is fully loaded with government staff members going to office this morning,” a source said.